decodeL8C2Qa
Decodes Landsat 8 Collection 2 Quality Assessment band conditions.

Parameters

value integer band pixel (16-bit value)



Examples
decodeL8C2Qa(55052);
// returns {
//   cirrus: 1, cirrusConfidence: 3,
//   clear: 0,
//   cloud: 1,
//   cloudConfidence: 3,
//   cloudShadow: 0,
//   cloudShadowConfidence: 1,
//   dilatedCloud: 0,
//   fill: 0,
//   snow: 0,
//   snowIceConfidence: 1,
//   water: 0
